LETHE — KeyguardAbsKeyInputView: apply staircase to timeoutMs.

Same change as the pattern view (0002): override the framework-default
timeoutMs with the LETHE staircase value after each failed unlock when
the prop is set. Covers PIN and password keyguards, which inherit from
this base class.

This view doesn't cache the KeyguardUpdateMonitor instance, so we use
getInstance(mContext) — matching the existing access at line 221 inside
getMessageWithCount.

Closes lethe#141.

--- a/packages/Keyguard/src/com/android/keyguard/KeyguardAbsKeyInputView.java
